Initialize Environment: Load the required libraries and input data files.
Extract GHA Data: Filter and select the relevant columns from the GHA dataset to create the GHA base data.
Standardize GHA Columns: Rename columns 'Position Number', 'Level 3', and 'Level 4' for uniformity.
Add Source Metadata: Insert an additional column to record the source file name.
Integrate Attrition Data: Match 'Employee ID' between the GHA base data and Attrition Report to extract 'Date of Leaving (DOL)' and update the GHA base data accordingly.
Extract Open Position Data: Select the required columns from the Open Position Report to create the Open Position base data.
Add Source Identifier: Create a new 'Source' column and populate it with the value 'Open Position'.
Standardize Column Names: Rename the column 'Position Number' to 'Position ID' in the Open Position base data.
Filter Taleo Data: Extract records from the Taleo Report where 'Requisition Source System' is 'Taleo'.
Select Taleo Columns: Filter and retain only the necessary columns from the Taleo Report.
Standardize Taleo Columns: Rename 'Requisition Number' to 'Taleo ID' and 'Position Number' to 'Position ID'.
Merge Taleo and Open Position Data: Perform an inner join on 'Position ID' to merge Taleo data with the Open Position base data.
Extract HR Input Data: Select the relevant columns from the HR Input file and standardize the 'Position Number' column to 'Position ID'.
Merge HR Input Data: Merge the updated Open Position base data with the HR Input data on 'Position ID'.
Identify Column Discrepancies: Identify additional columns required to align the GHA and Open Position datasets, ensuring a consistent schema.
Create Missing Columns: Add the necessary columns to both the GHA and Open Position datasets to maintain uniformity.
Set Column Order: Reorder columns as per the defined schema for both datasets.
Concatenate Datasets: Append the Open Position dataset to the GHA base data to form the final consolidated dataset.
Save Final Dataset: Export the combined data to a new file. Phase One Completed.
